1. BigVGAN: scratch (clean-room) reimplementation policy
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
CORRECTION (2026-07-22): the NVIDIA BigVGAN reference is **no longer**
non-commercial. github.com/NVIDIA/BigVGAN now ships a standard MIT license
("MIT License / Copyright (c) 2024 NVIDIA CORPORATION"), and the released
weights (e.g. nvidia/bigvgan_v2_24khz_100band_256x) declare `license: mit`.

The clean-room policy below was written when the reference was under the
