4. piper-plus (MB-iSTFT-VITS2 native TTS and G2P)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Vokra's native TTS (crates/vokra-models/src/piper_plus/*) is a from-scratch
Rust reimplementation of the MB-iSTFT-VITS2 inference core of piper-plus
(https://github.com/ayutaz/piper-plus), MIT-licensed. The voice model weights
are converted offline from the upstream piper-plus voices (also MIT). The G2P
(8-language text front-end) is bridged from piper-plus for now; the concrete
reuse form is pending (M0-07-T04, docs/piper-plus-integration.md), so the M0
build ships only a mock phonemizer and does not yet bundle piper-plus G2P.

